Marketing is what you do when your product is no good.

-Rolland, my father

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1" el_class=".textbg_col"][vc_column_text el_class=".textbg_ch" css=".vc_custom_1432738741433{margin-top: 87px !important;margin-bottom: 92px !important;}"]

My passion, woodworking, was passed to me by my grandfather, Rolland. Originally from Sweden, he met my grandmother, an Iraqi woman, in Irak. He was and still is the best woodworker I know.

Born in Irak and raised in England, I am now based in Darwin, Australia where I have many satisfied customers. My various trips around the globe to discover tropical wood species allow me to offer a wide range of different looks to your project.
